---
// Componente Sobre Nosotros
---

<section id="sobre-nosotros" class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-14 animate-fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-sans font-bold text-soft-white">Sobre <span class="text-orbe-violet">Nosotros</span></h2>
      <p class="mt-4 sm:mt-6 text-muted text-base sm:text-lg animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-200">Conoce más sobre nuestra historia, valores y compromiso con la excelencia</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Contenido de texto -->
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-300">
        <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
          <div class="hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white mb-3 sm:mb-4">Nuestra Filosofía</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Combinamos excelencia técnica con acompañamiento humano para que las personas no solo accedan a datos confiables, sino que también desarrollen la autonomía necesaria para crear sus propios proyectos y aplicar los conocimientos adquiridos, construyendo así un camino de información sostenible dentro de la organización.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white mb-3 sm:mb-4">Nuestro Impacto</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Al incorporar procesos inteligentes, ayudamos a tu organización a reducir drásticamente los tiempos operativos y a eliminar tareas repetitivas. Esto se traduce en un uso más eficiente del tiempo y los recursos, liberando a los equipos para que puedan enfocarse en actividades de mayor valor, innovación y análisis estratégico.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white mb-3 sm:mb-4">Nuestro Compromiso</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Impulsamos una cultura organizacional orientada a los datos, donde la información fluye de manera integrada, confiable y trazable a lo largo de todo su recorrido. Nuestro objetivo es transformar no solo los sistemas, sino también las personas que los utilizan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Elemento visual — data viz SVG -->
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-400">
        <div class="relative hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orbe-violet/10 to-purple-600/10 border border-orbe-violet/20 flex items-center justify-center p-8 overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Decorative glow -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, rgba(121,78,186,0.15) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>

            <!-- Data visualization SVG — bar chart + trend line -->
            <svg viewBox="0 0 220 185" class="w-full max-w-[260px] relative z-10" aria-hidden="true">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="barGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#a78bfa" stop-opacity="0.9"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5b21b6" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <linearGradient id="areaFill" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#8B5CF6" stop-opacity="0.12"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8B5CF6" stop-opacity="0"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <filter id="glow" x="-30%" y="-80%" width="160%" height="260%">
                  <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur"/>
                  <feMerge><feMergeNode in="blur"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
                </filter>
              </defs>

              <!-- Grid lines -->
              <line x1="28" y1="48" x2="200" y2="48" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <line x1="28" y1="83" x2="200" y2="83" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <line x1="28" y1="118" x2="200" y2="118" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)" stroke-width="1"/>

              <!-- Bottom axis -->
              <line x1="28" y1="143" x2="200" y2="143" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.2)" stroke-width="1"/>

              <!-- Bars — thin -->
              <rect x="49"  y="95" width="14" height="48"  rx="2" fill="url(#barGrad)"/>
              <rect x="93"  y="68" width="14" height="75"  rx="2" fill="url(#barGrad)"/>
              <rect x="137" y="38" width="14" height="105" rx="2" fill="url(#barGrad)"/>
              <rect x="181" y="60" width="14" height="83"  rx="2" fill="url(#barGrad)"/>

              <!-- Area fill under curve -->
              <path
                d="M56,95 C71,86 85,78 100,68 C115,59 129,39 144,38 C159,37 173,53 188,60 L188,143 L56,143 Z"
                fill="url(#areaFill)"
              />

              <!-- Trend line — proper Catmull-Rom → Bezier -->
              <path
                d="M56,95 C71,86 85,78 100,68 C115,59 129,39 144,38 C159,37 173,53 188,60"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#c4b5fd"
                stroke-width="1.8"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                filter="url(#glow)"
              />

              <!-- Dots -->
              <circle cx="56"  cy="95" r="3.5" fill="#130d2a" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <circle cx="100" cy="68" r="3.5" fill="#130d2a" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <circle cx="144" cy="38" r="4.5" fill="#130d2a" stroke="#ede9fe" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
              <circle cx="188" cy="60" r="3.5" fill="#130d2a" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>

              <!-- Axis labels -->
              <text x="56"  y="160" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" font-family="monospace">Q1</text>
              <text x="100" y="160" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" font-family="monospace">Q2</text>
              <text x="144" y="160" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.38)" font-family="monospace">Q3</text>
              <text x="188" y="160" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" font-family="monospace">Q4</text>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative dots -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 sm:-top-4 sm:-right-4 w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 rounded-full bg-orbe-violet/30 animate-bounce"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 sm:-bottom-4 sm:-left-4 w-4 h-4 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-600/30 animate-bounce animation-delay-1000"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Estadísticas o números destacados -->
    <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <div class="text-center animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-500 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4 rounded-xl bg-orbe-violet/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 text-orbe-violet" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white">Procesos Claros</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-600 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4 rounded-xl bg-orbe-violet/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 text-orbe-violet" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white mb-2">Soporte Dedicado</h3>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted">Acompañamiento personalizado en cada proyecto</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-700 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4 rounded-xl bg-orbe-violet/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 text-orbe-violet" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 20h9M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white mb-2">Capacitación Usuario</h3>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted">Formación integral para tu equipo</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-800 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4 rounded-xl bg-orbe-violet/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 lg:w-8 lg:h-8 text-orbe-violet" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M3 3v18h18M7 12h4M7 8h4M7 16h4M15 8h2M15 12h2M15 16h2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-sans font-semibold text-soft-white mb-2">Decisiones Basadas en Evidencia</h3>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted">Análisis riguroso y datos confiables</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
